## 2. Sales Intelligence System (ACTIVE DEVELOPMENT)

### What It Is
AI-powered sales intelligence layer on top of Zoho CRM for 20 sales reps + managers + founder.

### Three Core Functions
1. **Prioritize** — AI ranks leads (Hot/Warm/Cold) with reasons, daily call list
2. **Research & Advise** — On-demand company research + CRM analysis + close strategy
3. **Alert & Report** — Daily morning briefs, stale lead alerts, weekly reports via WhatsApp + Email

### Tech Stack
| Layer | Tool |
|-------|------|
| Agent Brain | LangGraph (Python) |
| LLM Primary | Claude Sonnet 4.5 |
| LLM Scoring | Claude Haiku 4.5 |
| LLM Fallback | GPT-4o |
| Backend | FastAPI (Python) |
| Database | Supabase (PostgreSQL + pgvector) |
| Frontend | React + TypeScript + Vite + Tailwind + shadcn/ui |
| Auth | Supabase Auth |
| CRM | Zoho CRM REST API v8 |
| WhatsApp | Gupshup |
| Email | Resend |
| Hosting | Railway (backend) + Vercel (frontend) |
| Monitoring | LangSmith |

### Current State (Feb 15, 2026)
- **Database:** Schema designed (12 tables), migrations created, pgvector enabled
- **Backend:** FastAPI scaffolded with all route files, LangGraph agents written (daily pipeline, research, assignment, weekly report), Zoho sync service, email/WhatsApp services, scheduler
- **Frontend:** React app scaffolded with 10 pages (Login, Dashboard, Manager Dashboard, Leads, Lead Detail, Briefs, Analytics, Alerts, Admin, Settings), layout components (Sidebar, Header), auth context, API client
- **Docs:** System design v2.0, Zoho integration spec, database schema, LangGraph agents spec, 10-week build plan

